longBusinessSummary: Taiwan Line Tek Electronic Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells electronic wiring sets, signal cables, and power cord sets in Asia, Europe, and America. The company primarily engages in the manufacture of various computer system power transmission line sets and electrical appliances; and processing and trading of power transmission line sets, information peripheral product signal connection lines, and connection line sets of communication systems. It also provides AC power cords for computers, telecommunications, consumer electronics, and power tools, as well as lighting and medical equipment applications. In addition, the company provides DC cables comprising AC products, such as computer and electrical appliance power supply cord sets; DC products consisting of signal connection cables for computers and peripherals, and telecommunication transmission cable accessories; electronic ballasts and electronic switch controllers; and fiber optic passive components for audio, CD-Rom, cell charge, cell phone, digital camcorder, digital camera, DVD, game machine, headphones, joystick, keyboard, LCD monitor, mouse, MP3, network, notebook, PDA, print, projector, speaker, telephone, TV, and VCR applications. The company was founded in 1967 and is based in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
longName: Taiwan Line Tek Electronic Co., Ltd.
